{
  "stem": "321.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But they were not given orders to resist, do anything about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So the police was not difficult, not bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they gave her the information, as far as they knew, that the people in that area were taken to Sachsenhausen.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "When we contacted my aunts, they found out that Eric and my uncle were there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They already had affidavits for America, although they wanted to go to England, you know, so that we would be together.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And because they had the affidavits, after about-- I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Before I left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So it could have not been between the 9th of December and 10th of-- November and December.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "About within that three and 1/2 week period, they were released because they had the affidavit and the ticket.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Somebody got them, you know, the ticket on the Manhattan to go to America.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And what happened was that they released those people who had possibilities of leaving the country at that time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I remember going in the middle of the night with my mother to meet the-- to meet them off the train.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I didn't recognize my uncle and my cousin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Their heads, of course, were shorn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And it was very cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And they had lost all their body weight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I just didn't recognize either of them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They were hanging out of the windows at the railroad station, and I did not recognize them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They were unrecognizable.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
